About Sonic Origins Pocket Edition

Sonic Origins Pocket Edition is a new take on the classic Sonic the Hedgehog franchise. This mobile game is designed for both casual and hardcore gamers alike and brings together elements from various Sonic games of the past. The game features an array of iconic characters, including Sonic, Tails, Knuckles, and Amy Rose, all with their unique abilities and moves.

The game is set in a 2D side-scrolling environment and features classic Sonic platforming gameplay, with players running, jumping, and collecting rings. The graphics have been updated to bring the game up to modern standards while still retaining the classic look and feel of the original games.

The game includes a variety of levels, each with its own unique challenges and obstacles to overcome. These levels are set in different locations, such as Green Hill Zone, Chemical Plant Zone, and Ice Cap Zone, among others.
